How to setup/install OpenMRS
- Copy the openmrs.war file to (Tomcat9.0/webapp)
- Create database under name: openmrs
- Create user with credential as: username: openmrs_user password: secret

- Run Tomcat service
- Open browser and enter following path: http://localhost:8080/openmrs
- Follow the wizard and setup the proper options using Advanced installation option.
- Set Login user credentials as: admin/Admin123

- stop the tomcat service after completion the openmrs installation
- Copy the Module and owa folder to (Application Data/OpenMRS/ or ~/.OpenMRS/)
- If error occours then stop the tomcat service and delete the logfiles of tomcat and restart the tomcat service

- You will see the login page of OpenMRS... successfully setup

